<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧٦٣- عَبد رَبِّه بن أَبي يَزِيد، أو ابن يَزِيد.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنْ أَبي عِياض.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوَى عَنه قَتادة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قال عليّ:</span> عَرَفَهُ ابن عُيَينَةَ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> كَانَ يَبيع الثِّياب.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>نَسَبَهُ هَمّام.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>